  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>原创 <span>每日发现最新LLM</span> <span>2026-03-09 18:31</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">中国香港</span></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=91609b50&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FUibyxhuYSuFbr1hZibgox1QZ4icXEnuEqYbPdiaPvHvsAKmJA9zS6r5QH4asNhjW0Z7RwvDzCeTb9t5NuWibkwb6AIKH5ndKfpLibySvTSlhrl6Jw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p>强大的图像编辑基础模型FireRed-Image-Edit，开源框架LTX-2.3，增强版本Nanbeige4.1，统一范式推进通用科学研究智能UniScientist，突破性的视频生成模型Helios，由AI Agent自动进行研究的项目autoresearch，可扩展且具有成本效益的框架REDSearcher</p>\n  <div style=\"text-align: left;line-height: normal;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"line-height: normal;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 3 []\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.0859375\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;width: 389px;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100010333\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=17b00053&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwuWicsSRFbFewfePZ1EiaVdtFvrJflfNa3P11kpGn8dhrOaAmmKQ3INqCXFZr2IrrUmmtkia9otecsw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif\"></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 0px;\"><mp-common-profile class=\"custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe mp_common_widget\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"机器之心SOTA模型\" data-alias=\"sotaai\" data-from=\"2\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/GU2ibjU7TDkyqTqr59u8fKegUibXxHSW3WF3ib6u8lQO8JicgNbPzicmhb8kPjrkYk6libDSD7ia1RlxQN9bWugwjguOg/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"追踪 AI 开源进展，探索先进开发实践。\" data-id=\"MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==\"></mp-common-profile></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;text-indent: 0px;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：FireRed-Image-Edit</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-height=\"908\" data-imgfileid=\"100018097\" data-ratio=\"0.5675925925925925\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ec8d12db&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFZWkaY4Q5ibMhGvVdWCtZP8HTjWUzzkrFiaUGCibibrFicCIwgxQBSHOokMwH6qjTfmLgtlrVKicthNPKRIpfGkd0QG8M6yz1UFM7bibE%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★FireRed-Image-Edit是一个强大的图像编辑基础模型，提供开源的最先进性能，具备精确的指令跟随、高保真的生成、卓越的身份一致性以及无缝的多元素融合。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目在多种场景下提供高质量和一致的编辑效果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/firered-image-edit\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/firered-image-edit</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：LTX-2.3</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5351851851851852\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"857\" data-imgfileid=\"100018096\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ee47d0d4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFY1j5iaibKfWMc6crwT1ynD4pWiahsAicpS1DqIicbAlE7x1WopWOKRN9WtNZ6y6xGzaExuIqNXtM55lhmU1eL9vTtKbTBL5PichYvak%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★LTX-2.3是Lightricks推出的一款聚焦于移动端高性能图像处理与渲染的开源框架，专为满足移动场景下对图像编辑、特效处理的极致性能与灵活扩展需求而设计。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">它的核心设计理念是兼顾</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">移动端的资源约束</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">与</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">视觉效果的高品质</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，通过轻量化的架构设计和硬件加速优化，在手机等低功耗设备上实现媲美专业级的图像算法执行效率。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/ltx-2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/ltx-2</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：Nanbeige4.1</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.687037037037037\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"1099\" data-imgfileid=\"100018095\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2ed29525&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFamRTu6icVK6NbGTGTYicIynrNxXguX3Sv9O4UvAZyO9VwicaS1RM0aLG8BBs8dzCwMEELoInZqicEEpZRnVxxHXr8aicpCXBj1ibYmA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Nanbeige4.1是基于Nanbeige4-Base构建的增强版本，通过监督微调和强化学习进行后期优化。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">作为一个小参数规模的开源模型，Nanbeige4.1展示了紧凑模型在推理、偏好对齐和Agent行为方面的强大能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/nanbeige4-1\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/nanbeige4-1</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">④项目：UniScientist</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5546296296296296\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"887\" data-imgfileid=\"100018094\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3e203b33&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFbsYmabIGbicZGqibyibLyNTSoF4cZPdrZbAnzKd0IOsT31pthKgMD6s3AzQ8a6YibPwfsnkSNNEQSSQxQGEoKXyv0gHedBpOPvCHU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★UniScientist通过统一范式推进通用科学研究智能。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目将大型语言模型（LLMs）重新定义为</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">跨学科生成器</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，并将人类专家作为高精度验证者，生成涵盖50多个科学学科的研究级数据。一个基于这些数据训练的30B参数模型在五个研究基准上表现出高度竞争力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/uniscientist\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/uniscientist</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">⑤项目：Helios</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.39444444444444443\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"631\" data-imgfileid=\"100018102\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7b5914eb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFYjp0Gb6MON3RBgHUYJZYMiaJg1SibS0uibRNlw4FdCBpuGITbBhWQtbov89l0TZ5ehv0bSXicFaYgWc2T5vX1ZiayFnxUyYibSpbtkI%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Helios是一个突破性的视频生成模型，能够在单个H100 GPU上以19.5 FPS的速度生成分钟级高质量视频，而无需依赖传统的长视频防漂移策略或标准视频加速技术。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型通过优化训练和推理吞吐量，同时减少内存消耗，实现了图像扩散级别的批量大小训练，并在80 GB的GPU内存中容纳多达四个14B模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/helios\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/helios</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;text-indent: 0px;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️ 框架平台、必备工具</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：autoresearch</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5064814814814815\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"810\" data-imgfileid=\"100018101\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=773f6611&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFaM325ZtVVSAGo2ojKk8n91SdplxEPFOjbAp5LcYCTibVwyNo1X3qr5tqGUgbZxwBB8wQ3Dq5qric4jhnoktGroBlicmibzuPO1QTs%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★autoresearch是一个由AI Agent自动进行研究的项目，旨在通过单GPU实现小规模但真实的语言模型训练。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">Agent会</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">自主修改代码</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，进行短时间训练，评估结果并决定保留或丢弃实验。项目的核心是通过</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">编写Markdown文件</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">来设置Agent的研究环境，而不是直接修改Python文件。此项目提供了一种创新的方式来加速研究进程。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/autoresearch\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/autoresearch</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：REDSearcher</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5740740740740741\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"919\" data-imgfileid=\"100018100\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c377b709&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFZ1zqQDKJf8Wy4Mz7dTdmFvarZEY1FYdWl6GNsfo1YySc2cNzDofPPpYkggDE25lHVicZsOLbNFU6WX6HeQzQ1CfBgNibWObZh2Y%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★REDSearcher是一个可扩展且具有成本效益的框架，专为长期搜索Agent而设计。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目旨在通过</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">集成多种技术和方法</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，提升搜索Agent在复杂任务中的表现。其核心在于优化资源使用和提高搜索效率，适用于需要长时间和大规模数据处理的应用场景。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, 